  \## What is Swagger?

%section{"data-markdown" => ""}
  \### Swagger is a representation for REST APIs:

  * Interactive documentation
  * Client SDK generation
  * Discoverability
  * Supporting many programming languages and environments
  * 100% Open Source

%section{"data-markdown" => ""}
  \### What's Open Source in this case?

%section{"data-markdown" => ""}

  \#### 2011-08-10: First release of the Swagger Specification

  To bring the “good parts” of REST, SOAP, Web Services and RPC into a simple, easy to understand format.

%section{"data-markdown" => ""}
  \#### 2014-09-08:	Release of Swagger 2.0

  Swagger tools are downloaded close to 15,000 times per day.
