  \### Describing APIs in Swagger

%section
  %h4 A 'hello world' API
  %pre
    %code
      :preserve
        swagger: "2.0"
        info:
          version: "1.0"
          title: "Hello World API"
        paths:
          /hello/{user}:
            get:
              description: Returns a greeting to the user!
              parameters:
                - name: user
                  in: path
                  type: string
                  required: true
                  description: The name of the user to greet.
              responses:
                200:
                  description: Returns the greeting.
                  schema:
                    type: string
                400:
                  description: Invalid characters in "user" were provided.
